Package tellosimulator.model

Class DroneModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • tellosimulator.model.DroneModel
  • public class DroneModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The model class holding all the data of the virtual drone. Controlled by the logic from the DroneController, and represented in the 3D-Scene by the DroneView.
    See Also:
    DroneController, DroneView
